Title: Add host name completion in different places
Level: 1
Component: multisite
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.6.0b1
Date: 1545206237
Class: feature

When entering host names in different places, like for example the parent attribute fields of a host
or the nodes fields of a cluster host, a dropdown is shown with the host names matching the already
inserted hostname parts. You may klick on the matching hostname to add it to the input field.
